ce\nTelescope (JWST) to probe high-redshift (U)LIRGs into their nuclear regions\nwhere JWST will be limited by its resolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Aug 2018 08:50:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Oct 2018 03:41:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-31"}
