ization of the superatom model demonstrated for spherical shapes ten\nyears ago (Walter et al., PNAS 2008, 105, 9157).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Aug 2018 13:09:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-21"}
